pointer, or RTS-trick reference reaches any address in
[[$1F19--$1FFD]]; the code is unreachable during gameplay.

The logic mirrors the current [[HANDLE_MOB_ENCOUNTER]] almost exactly:
threat assessment (strength~$+$~16~$-$~threats, clamped 4\ldots28,
